ence diagram isn't included in the hints list yet—I should add that to be thorough.\n\nThe knowledge file matches the source code well with all the main classes present. The user examples with Yさん and Dさん are illustrative details that don't need to be in the knowledge file, so that's fine.\n\nNow I'm comparing the exact wording between the knowledge file and source more carefully. The knowledge file simplifies \"認可単位を保持したテーブル構造から\" to \"認可単位テーブルから\" - it's a minor condensation rather than an inaccuracy. The only real gap I've found is that missing `ThreadContextHandler` reference in the s4 hints.\n\nLooking back at the source's 構成/概念モデル section to make sure I haven't overlooked anything critical...\n\nthe knowledge file captures the key concepts and references the images appropriately, though it doesn't include specific examples like the Yさん note from the user table—but that's fine since those are just illustrative. The only real gap I'm finding is that `ThreadContextHandler` should be included in the s4 hints since it's referenced as a class name in the sequence diagram section. Otherwise, the knowledge file is solid and accurate.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23091,"cache_read_input_tokens":29873,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":23091,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"427b757d-8255-4474-9b42-72c265b97e3c","uuid":"6d7c2901-acdd-49c5-98e3-976b2c20f659"}
